snippet.title: Split/Second announcement trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.facebook.com/splitsecond

From the creators of Pure, here's a first look at their latest, offering the highly action-packed arcade racer SPLIT/SECOND where speed meets strategy in a hyper-competitive reality TV series with the ultimate goal of emerging as the season champion.

Visit the official Split/Second  website at http://www.splitsecondvideogame.com
